            <div class="isi-content preview-text">
			
                <div class="gateway-indication-head orphanHide"><div class="head3 head-title boldtext mb-25">INDICATIONS</div>
<p class="bodypara">ZEPOSIA<sup>®</sup> (ozanimod) is indicated for the treatment of:</p>
<ol class="mb-24">
<li class="bodypara">Relapsing forms of multiple sclerosis (MS), to include clinically isolated syndrome, relapsing-remitting disease, and active secondary progressive disease, in adults.</li>
<li class="bodypara mt-24-top">Moderately to severely active ulcerative colitis (UC) in adults.</li>
</ol>
</div>

